@startuml
title Feature 012 - создание и обработка претензии
actor User as U
participant "Claims UI" as UI
participant "OrderClaimController" as C
participant "OrderClaimService" as S
participant "Order history" as OH
participant "Warehouse/Logistics" as WL
participant "Payment" as P
U -> UI: выбирает заказ и позиции
UI -> C: POST /api/order/claims
C -> S: createClaim(user, request, idempotencyKey)
S -> OH: load order details and claimable lines
OH --> S: order, lines, prices, claimAvailable
S -> S: validate, calculate refund, create audit events
S --> C: OrderClaimDetailsResponse
C --> UI: claimId, status, refundAmount, mnemonic codes
UI --> U: показывает результат
S -> WL: route warehouse/logistics check when required
WL --> S: check result event
S -> P: send approved refund when resolution is REFUND
P --> S: refund status event
S --> UI: updated claim details on refresh
@enduml